&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;bin&#x2F;docker-compose down&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;&lt;h1 id=&quot;wan-zheng-an-zhuang-bu-zou&quot;&gt;完整安装步骤&lt;&#x2F;h1&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;prepare-dns&quot;&gt;Prepare DNS&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;giallo&quot; style=&quot;color: #FFFFFF; background-color: #262335;&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-lang=&quot;plain&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;giallo-l&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;# Create a wildcard A record pointing to the public IP of your VM. As an example, *.netmaker.example.com. Alternatively, create records for these specific subdomains:&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
